                     <incipit xml:lang="ar">
                        <locus target="#?">-?</locus>Lakk. M/01/2/16
Guyyaa 21/01/95

Waajjira bulchaa ganda Booree Gaw[raaf?] 

Dhimmi isaa [.?.] Sosochii daa'iwaa ulamootaa ni ta'a- 
Kilaafii gandaa fi masjiida keessanitti argama jedhome Qur- 
aanaa fi haadiisaan hiikuuf[?] ulamootni guyyaa 27[/1/95?] [.?.] 
daa'iwaaf waan ganda keessan dhufanuuf ummatni musliima ta'e mara masjiida meeroo tti akka argamanu addeessaa, kanaan booda eehama(daaggoo) majlis al-ulamaa'i Ykn waajjira dhi/Iskamummaa aanaa Gommaa irraa utuu hin argatin masjiida keessatti waa'izii gochum akka hin danda' [anmnee?] fi namni se- 
era kana darbe rakkina dhufuuf akka itti gaafatamu ni hubachiisna. 
Nagaa wajjin 

HمحمدLA

Bakka - H/Tamaam A/Raagoo</incipit>
